train=sample(1:nrow(algae), 100)
algae.test <- algae[-train,]
algae.train <- algae[train,]

tree <- ctree(a1 ~ ., data = algae.train)

plot(tree)

plot(tree, type = "simple")

plot(tree, gp = gpar(fontsize = 6),     # font size changed to 6
      inner_panel=node_inner,
      ip_args=list(
        abbreviate = F,

        pval=F)
 )

     type = "simple"
 )
